com.paypal.selion.platform.html

  • Packages that use com.paypal.selion.platform.html 
    Package Description
    com.paypal.selion.platform.html
    Classes that provide an abstraction to all the HTML elements used in SeLion.
    com.paypal.selion.platform.html.support
    Contains the customized location strategy for identifying web elements.
    com.paypal.selion.platform.utilities
    Contains the common set of utilities to assist in writing tests using SeLion.
    com.paypal.selion.testcomponents
    Contains re-usable page object components for testing.
  • Classes in com.paypal.selion.platform.html used by com.paypal.selion.platform.html

    AbstractElement
    Abstract element class for web elements.
    ParentTraits
    A generic interface for outlining the Parent traits of an HTML entity in SeLion.
    By Default, A Page BasicPageImpl is the parent to AbstractElement when loaded via SeLion.
    WebPage
    A generic interface for web Page Objects in SeLion.
